General Information
===================

Each directory contains some Promela source code, that could simulate
or verify some part of Verse protocol. Each directory could contain some
subdirectories concerned to some subproblem. Spin program is used
for simulation and verification. Spin could be downloaded from:

  http://http://spinroot.com/

To simulate some simplified part of Verse protocol go to a directory
containing Makefile and type:

  make sim

To verify this part of Verse protocol type:

  make ver

Keep in mind that verification of some parts of Verse protocol could
require lot of memory and can take few minutes.